<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>电视台的每个人都在忙碌着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女人把摄像机打开了，一个男人把话筒搬了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在准备开拍新一集的《大力士》。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大力士在哪儿？”有人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这儿呢。”一个穿着超级英雄服装的演员说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然间——砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人出现在烟雾中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他戴着一顶高高的帽子，嘴上留着细细的胡子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着礼服，肩膀上有一只猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个男人邪恶地笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天会上演一出新的节目！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿！”杰克说，“十分钟后《大力士》就要开始了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们在去杰克家的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们要去看《大力士》，是一个关于超级英雄的电视剧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好奇大力士今天会干什么。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上周一个行星马上就要撞到地球了。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，今天大力士会阻止它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大力士真的是太酷了。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还可以吧。”特勒尔说，“他并不是特别厉害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和玛拉愣了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是什么意思？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大力士不是真的。他只是一个电视剧里面的演员。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们知道。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是如果他是真的，那他就是最棒的超级英雄。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是不可能的！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿比大力士酷多了！对吗，罗西？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西。”玛拉说，“你是怎么想的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西想了想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意特勒尔的想法。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿比大力士酷多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大力士有点儿……傻。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四个朋友到了杰克的家，进了房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克拿了一些零食，然后大家坐在了沙发上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克打开了电视，但是《大力士》并没有开始。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>取而代之的是一个奇怪的男人在表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他戴着一顶高高的帽子，嘴上还有细细的胡子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家好。”那个男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“《大力士》被取消了。我将为大家表演一个新的节目。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是一个魔术表演，我是明星！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会变得非常有名的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是谁呀？”特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西知道那个男人是谁，但是她没有办法告诉她的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘那是邪恶的魔术师普雷斯托！’她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她冲到杰克家的厨房，按下了手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”布洛姆市长说，“普雷斯托占领了整个电视台！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”罗西小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用担心，我会阻止他的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>